# Blank Study

> Shared study tab patterns: see `study-feature-tab.mdc`.

Blank study is NOT flashcards and NOT per-item Card UI. Use workbook-style active recall with inline blank inputs in a continuous text flow:

```txt
N개 노드 트리의 간선 수는 ______ 이다. BST에서 왼쪽 자식은 현재 키보다 ______ 값을 가진다.
```

Do NOT render blanks as a numbered list (`1.` `2.` …). Group by section label if needed, then flow sentences in a single `<p>`.

**On-demand**: blanks are generated only when the user clicks generate (not on upload).

**Generate options** (`BlankGeneratePanel`):

| Option | Values | Notes |
|--------|--------|-------|
| 출처 | `pdf` \| `explanation` | PDF 원문 vs already-generated 강의 노트 |
| 범위 | `all` \| `chapter` \| `page` | **PDF 출처일 때만** show/apply |
| 밀도 | `light` \| `normal` \| `dense` | mock item count |

**Source rules**:

- `pdf`: use stored PDF extracted text (`MaterialPdfText`) — punch blanks from original sentences (not handcrafted seeds)
- `explanation`: extract from `LectureExplanation` (core concepts, exam highlights, etc.)
- If source=`explanation` and no explanation exists → **block generate** + CTA link to 쉽게 설명 tab (no auto-fallback)

**Result UI** (`BlankStudyResultView`): progress bar, continuous prose with inline blanks, hint/feedback, retry incorrect, **[저장]** to confirm hybrid edits — no Card wrapper, no numbered list.

**Hint**: show on **hover/focus** (not click toggle). Sentence-style contextual hint.

**Grading**: `normalizeAnswer` — trim, lowercase, strip special chars, exact match (case-insensitive).

**Hybrid save**: AI generate → user click-to-blank edits → **[저장]** persists session (`saveBlankSession`).

## Components

- `BlankGeneratePanel` — generate options + empty/result shell
- `BlankStudyResultView` — progress, prose, retry
- `BlankProseSection` — inline blank flow in `<p>`
- `BlankPdfProseView`, `BlankSelectableText` — PDF-source prose + custom blank mode

## Key files

- Hook: `src/features/blank-study/hooks/useBlankStudy.ts`
- Types: `src/types/blank-study.ts`
- Mocks: `src/lib/mocks/blank-study.ts`, `src/lib/mocks/blank-study-content.ts`
- Logic: `src/lib/blank-study/` (build, tokenize, add/remove custom blank)
- Route: `src/app/(app)/study/[id]/blank-study/page.tsx`

For large blank-study work, use `.cursor/skills/blank-study/SKILL.md`.
